data.title: Rose “Rosie” Valentino Pittman (1928
data.meta_description: Rose Valentino-Pittman passed away Monday, December 12, 2005 at the age of 77 in Haven Hospice at John F. Kennedy Medical Center in Edison, New Jersey.  Born and raised in the Ironbound section of Newark, New Jersey, Rose moved with her husband Vernon Pittman and their children to Edison, New Jersey in 1968 where she...
